{"handle": "JFlotrades", "profile": {"username": "JFlotrades", "name": "Jeremy F", "avatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43, "verified": true, "restId": "2008945880670613504"}, "history": [{"date": "2026-07-15", "followers": 7, "following": 9, "tweets": 39}, {"date": "2026-07-16", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 40}, {"date": "2026-07-17", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}, {"date": "2026-07-18", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}, {"date": "2026-07-19", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}, {"date": "2026-07-20", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}, {"date": "2026-07-21", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}, {"date": "2026-07-22", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}, {"date": "2026-07-23", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}, {"date": "2026-07-24", "followers": 8, "following": 9, "tweets": 43}], "posts": [{"id": "2008985283434332162", "text": "Hi, I’m Jeremy\n\nI started trading ICT concept in October but been trading for 5 years now. I’m using X to document my trades. I believe in truth and transparency. I’ll be posting up all my trades and explanations. Whether it is a win or a loss so I can learn better.\n\nI mainly trade NQ but I also trade other markets as well using this model:\n- Key level sweeps (Asia/London/PD highs & lows)\n- IFVG\n- SMT", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFlotrades", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 8, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 5, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 59, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-07T19:33:11+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFlotrades/status/2008985283434332162"}, {"id": "2078222700951003629", "text": "Trust the process. It always pays in due time https://t.co/j9q4qbPQp7", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFlotrades", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 8, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 4, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 35, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-07-17T20:57:58+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFlotrades/status/2078222700951003629"}, {"id": "2077861615983096055", "text": "Two trades today.\n\nTook a -$270 on the first. Didn't chase it, didn't revenge trade. Just cut it.\n\nWaited for orderflow to give me a clean read, and the second one paid +$774.\n\nSmall losses, bigger winners. That's the model. Green day 🟢 https://t.co/ZI9mFqPwDQ", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFlotrades", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 8, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 5, "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 46, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-07-16T21:03:08+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFlotrades/status/2077861615983096055"}, {"id": "2022362094763708727", "text": "The importance of risk management. January was a hard month for me; it almost wiped me out. https://t.co/qN3fUa4xYg", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFlotrades", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 8, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 3, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 1, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 27, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-02-13T17:27:51+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFlotrades/status/2022362094763708727"}, {"id": "2022362097296834652", "text": "February has been better; I'm locked in. Keeping my losses small and my winners big. That is the true essence of being a profitable trader. Don't need